Invocation Name: osaka guide
des: This application will help you plan your next trip to Osaka, Japan. Learn about various attractions in the area as well as the top five things to do in Osaka from a recent traveler to the area. Additionally, you can get a brief overview of the area and even get local news for Osaka from the New York Times API.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
